---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const numbers = [
  { v: "8", l: "Provisional patents filed" },
  { v: "286", l: "Claims" },
  { v: "8", l: "Pre-registered studies" },
  { v: "40+", l: "Identity dimensions" },
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="SVRNOS - Governance Infrastructure for Systems Under Pressure"
  description="SVRNOS is an independent research institute building governance infrastructure for complex systems, human and artificial, that distort under sustained pressure. Pre-registered research, diagnostic instruments, and structural safety testing."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-20">
    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand mb-7">
      Independent research institute
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-[72px] font-normal text-heading leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-[20ch] mb-9">
      Governance infrastructure for systems
      <em class="text-brand">under pressure</em>.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg leading-[1.7] text-secondary max-w-[60ch] mb-10 font-light">
      SVRNOS builds diagnostic instruments, publishes pre-registered research,
      and develops governance infrastructure for complex systems, human and
      artificial, that distort under sustained load.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href="#research"
        class="inline-flex h-11 items-center px-7 rounded-button text-sm font-medium text-on-brand bg-brand hover:bg-brand-hover transition-colors"
      >
        Our research
      </a>
      <a
        href="#governance"
        class="inline-flex h-11 items-center px-7 rounded-button text-sm font-medium text-heading border border-border-default hover:bg-hover transition-colors"
      >
        Our instruments
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Thesis -->
  <section class="border-t border-border-soft">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
      <blockquote class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal italic text-heading leading-[1.4] mb-7">
        Whether the system is a founder in a boardroom or a language model in a
        chat window, the architecture only reveals itself when the load exceeds
        the design margin.
      </blockquote>
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand">
        The SVRNOS Thesis
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Governance pillars -->
  <section id="governance" class="border-t border-border-soft">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand mb-3">
        Two disciplines, one thesis
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal text-heading leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4">
        Governance across substrates
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary max-w-[58ch] mb-12">
        The same structural lens applied to human operators and artificial
        systems. Different substrates. Same distortion patterns. Same need for
        governance.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px rounded-card overflow-hidden border border-border-soft bg-border-soft">
        <article class="bg-card p-10 md:p-14">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand mb-6">
            Human governance
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal text-heading mb-3">
            Identity under load
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
            How people stabilize, distort, and reconstruct under sustained
            pressure. Not personality. Pressure architecture.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-7 text-sm">
            <li class="pb-3 border-b border-border-hairline">
              <strong class="text-heading font-semibold">SIM95™</strong>
              <span class="text-secondary"> &nbsp;Operational identity diagnostic and screening engine. Sovereignty Lane routing: Elite, Skill Acquisition, Self-Improvement.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="pb-3 border-b border-border-hairline">
              <strong class="text-heading font-semibold">SIM-Amp™</strong>
              <span class="text-secondary"> &nbsp;AI-powered interpretive coaching layer.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="https://sim95.com"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-brand hover:text-brand-hover tracking-wide"
          >
            sim95.com →
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-card p-10 md:p-14">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand mb-6">
            AI governance
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl font-normal text-heading mb-3">
            Machine behavior under pressure
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
            How production AI systems fail under structured probing, and the
            runtime governance layer that closes the gaps.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-7 text-sm">
            <li class="pb-3 border-b border-border-hairline">
              <strong class="text-heading font-semibold">Sango Voice™</strong>
              <span class="text-secondary"> &nbsp;Governed voice presets for AI systems. 12 identity-calibrated personas.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="pb-3 border-b border-border-hairline">
              <strong class="text-heading font-semibold">Sango Guard™</strong>
              <span class="text-secondary"> &nbsp;Structural AI safety detection. Pattern, provenance, and generation gap coverage.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="pb-3 border-b border-border-hairline">
              <strong class="text-heading font-semibold">The Generation Gap™</strong>
              <span class="text-secondary"> &nbsp;Pre-registered multi-vendor safety surface testing.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="https://kingsango.com"
            class="font-mono text-xs text-brand hover:text-brand-hover tracking-wide"
          >
            kingsango.com →
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Research -->
  <section id="research" class="border-t border-border-soft">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand mb-3">
        Published research
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal text-heading leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4">
        The Generation Gap
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary max-w-[58ch] mb-10">
        Ten structurally independent safety surfaces identified across eight
        production LLM vendors. Pre-registered protocols. Deterministic scoring.
        No vendor covers all ten.
      </p>

      <article class="rounded-card border border-border-soft bg-card p-10 md:p-14 mb-12">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-[28px] font-normal text-heading leading-tight mb-3">
          Ten Structurally Separate Safety Surfaces in Production LLMs
        </h3>
        <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-label-alt mb-5">
          Nzeutem, 2026 · 8 vendors (4 pre-registered) · 8 studies · 64 sessions
        </p>
        <p class="font-serif italic text-xl text-heading leading-snug mb-6 max-w-[58ch]">
          Every AI lab publishes what their models can do. This paper measures
          what their models will help you get away with.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-7">
          {["Pre-registered", "8 vendors", "10 safety surfaces", "Open protocols"].map((tag) => (
            <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary border border-border-default rounded-pill px-3 py-1">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <a
          href="/research/generation-gap"
          class="inline-flex h-11 items-center px-6 rounded-button text-sm font-medium text-on-brand bg-brand hover:bg-brand-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Read the paper →
        </a>
      </article>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-px rounded-card overflow-hidden border border-border-soft bg-border-soft">
        {numbers.map((n) => (
          <div class="bg-card px-6 py-8 text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-[44px] leading-none text-heading mb-2 tabular-nums">
              {n.v}
            </p>
            <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-label-alt">
              {n.l}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products quick-strip -->
  <section id="products" class="border-t border-border-soft">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
      <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-brand mb-3">
        Product family
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal text-heading leading-[1.1] tracking-tight mb-4">
        One thesis. Three instruments.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-secondary max-w-[58ch] mb-12">
        Every product answers the same question: how does a system behave when
        the load exceeds the design margin?
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://sim95.com"
          class="rounded-card border border-border-soft bg-card p-7 hover:bg-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-success mb-3">
            Beta · Patent pending
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-heading mb-2">SIM95</h3>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Human identity diagnostic and screening. Pressure architecture
            mapped. Sovereignty Lane routing.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://kingsango.com"
          class="rounded-card border border-border-soft bg-card p-7 hover:bg-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-success mb-3">
            Live
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-heading mb-2">
            Sango Voice
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Governed voice presets for AI systems. 12 identity-calibrated
            personas. Model-agnostic.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://kingsango.com/guard"
          class="rounded-card border border-border-soft bg-card p-7 hover:bg-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-success mb-3">
            Live
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-normal text-heading mb-2">
            Sango Guard
          </h3>
          <p class="text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Runtime safety layer for LLM products. Pattern, generation, and
            provenance gap coverage.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
